Wait time

Custom: If your order is custom,  we'll need a calendar month to complete your order. Thanks in advance for your patience!

Stock: If you purchased stock and accessories your purchase will be in the mail within three working days.

Shipping and pick-up info

You will receive shipping confirmation when the parcel is on its way. International Shipping is sent through USPS. USPS does not offer international tracking, but you will receive a shipping confirmation email. For local pick up, we'll let you know when the bags are finished!

